ho does not have direct responsibility for the design stage being reviewed.","marks":[{"type":"italic"}]}]},{"type":"pageBreak"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"5. Design verification [820.30(f)]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Confirm that the design output meets the design input requirements. Results, including identification of the design, method(s), date, and individual(s) performing the verification, shall be documented in the DHF.","marks":[{"type":"italic"}]}]},{"type":"pageBreak"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"6. Design validation [820.30(g)]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ensure that devices conform to defined user needs and intended uses and shall include testing of production units under actual or simulated use conditions. Validation includes software validation and risk analysis, where appropriate.","marks":[{"type":"italic"}]}]},{"type":"pageBreak"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"7. Design transfer [820.30(h)]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Procedures to ensure that the device design is correctly translated into production specifications.","marks":[{"type":"italic"}]}]},{"type":"pageBreak"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"8. Design changes [820.30(i)]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Procedures for the identification, documentation, validation or where appropriate verification, review, and approval of design changes before their implementation.","marks":[{"type":"italic"}]}]},{"type":"pageBreak"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"9. Design history file [820.30(j)]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"DHF index — contains or references the records necessary to demonstrate that the design was developed in accordance with the approved 